            <abstract>
                <p>A treatise that explains the main concepts and terms of the Ethiopian calendar and computus.
                  The title is not always present in the beginning. The treatise is
                  composed of short subsections, many starting with words <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወካዕበ፡ በዘ፡ ታአምር፡</foreign>
                   The witnesses show significant variations.</p>
